Type: Time compression used - 1 second of game time equals 2 seconds of real time
Walk speeds are 2.5 mph for infantry limbered artillery and ordance 3.5 for cavalry and couriers
Walk and run speed for unlimbered artillery is 1/4 infantry walk speed
Run speed for all types except unlimbered artillery equals the types walk speed x2
